wdi-BM.GSR.MRCH.CD.def: Goods imports refer to all movable goods (including nonmonetary gold) involved in a change of ownership from nonresidents to residents. Data are in current U.S. dollars.
wdi-BM.GSR.MRCH.CD.name: Goods imports
wdi-BM.GSR.MRCH.CD.source: International Monetary Fund, Balance of Payments Statistics Yearbook and data files.
